  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/158654831/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u158654831-1.jpg" class="pil" alt="孤独的二太爷" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/158654831/">孤独的二太爷</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          6月21日          想读      </div>

      <br/>

